         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Philoxenos, strategos of the divisions of Themistos and Polemon of the Arsinoite nome, from Herodion and his associates, sitologoi-elect of the village of Tebtunis. There has been measured to us on the ..th of the present month Pharmouthi to the credit of Patron, ex-exegetes, (.. artabas) of wheat measured by the public smoothed measure, the sum of which he had the loan to pay for the collector's rates of the past . Year by order of his highness the epistrategos, Car�us Concessus, which have been dispatched to Sounio. .th year of Imperator Caesar Lucius Septimius Severus Pius Pertinax Augustus, Pharmouthi [.]</ab>
         </div>
